# AWS EKS RACI Matrix

## Legend
- **R** - Responsible (does the work)
- **A** - Accountable (ultimately answerable for the correct completion)
- **C** - Consulted (provides input/advice)
- **I** - Informed (kept up-to-date on progress)

## Teams
- **PCE** - Public Cloud Engineering Team
- **ENS** - Enterprise Network Services Team
- **EDW** - EKS Data Warehouse Team (your team)
- **MLOps** - MLOps Team
- **Shakudo** - Vendor (Shakudo)
- **Dynatrace** - Dynatrace Team
- **Aqua** - Aqua Security Team

---

