## Notes
- This matrix should be reviewed and updated regularly as responsibilities evolve
- Multiple teams may share R (Responsible) for complex activities requiring collaboration
- Vendor involvement (Shakudo) may vary based on support contract terms
- Consider creating separate matrices for different environments (dev, staging, prod) if responsibilities differ